{"type":"message","id":"820f5a27","parentId":"e2154a46","timestamp":"2026-03-08T10:01:07.259Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦，这个群叫\"思高乐教育\"，不是\"虾王群\"？不管了，先拉消息看看。\n\n现在用 feishu_im_user_get_messages 拉取这个群过去1小时内的消息。当前时间是 2026-03-08 18:00:00+08:00，所以 start_time 是 2026-03-08T17:00:00+08:00，end_time 是 2026-03-08T18:00:00+08:00。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1ticqxfpi5l2tow3v80tm0ct","name":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","arguments":{"chat_id":"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569","start_time":"2026-03-08T17:00:00+08:00","end_time":"2026-03-08T18:00:00+08:00","page_size":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1183,"output":295,"cacheRead":36664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38142,"cost":{"input":1.1830000000000001e-7,"output":5.9e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.773e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772964047237}}
