{"type":"message","id":"956b793b","parentId":"8f69a555","timestamp":"2026-03-08T10:01:35.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦，搜索结果是空的……看来过去1小时内这个群没有消息？或者是搜索的方式不对？\n\n或者……要不试试用 relative_time=last_1_hours？或者是不是时间范围的问题？\n\n或者……既然搜索结果是空的，那按照任务要求，如果没有有价值的内容就不发。\n\n不过等等，刚才用 feishu_im_user_get_messages 报错是应用类型不支持，用 feishu_im_user_search_messages 搜索结果是空的。那是不是确实没有消息？\n\n那按照任务要求，如果这一小时没有有价值的内容就不发。那本王应该回复什么？\n\n任务说\"如果这一小时没有有价值的内容就不发\"，那是不是应该回复 NO_REPLY？或者回复 HEARTBEAT_OK？不对，这是 cron 任务……\n\n等等，再看一下任务描述：\"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n\n如果没有有价值的内容，那应该不发，所以是不是应该回复 NO_REPLY？或者回复空？\n\n不过……再确认一下，是不是真的没有消息？要不试试把时间范围放宽一点，比如 last_2_hours？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_phycyfhiv25tr9qyq9s5w0vr","name":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","arguments":{"chat_id":"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569","relative_time":"last_2_hours","page_size":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":749,"output":372,"cacheRead":37944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39065,"cost":{"input":7.49e-8,"output":7.44e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.493e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772964081825}}
